column5: See what happens when you get older Hit the link below and remeber when. http://www.marycy.org:80/remember.html
I'm not one for much of twang twang music, my beer dried  up and my dog peed on my foot, but that was definitely nice.  Now I'm going fo rthe afternoon old age snooze.
